race.comment: STYLISH FLIPPER (7) finished fifth at his last appearance here on December 20 after he got a long way back in the run. Finds a suitable assignment this time and is a great chance to break throug at what will be start number four. Surely closer in running now. SECOND HEAVEN (11) is a Ribchester filly on debut for the smart juvenile stable of R & C Jolly. Has impressed in her lead-up work and gets in light with the claimer sticking. Can make an immediate impact. NIC THE CASH (1) carries a fitness edge and looks best of the rest. Thought SUMMERTIME MADNESS (4) ran well fresh and has nice upside. Tricky draw perhaps but tipping we see a nice run.
